{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-programs-js","path":"/programs/webhooks.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Webhooks enable you to build your own real-time integrations that subscribe to certain report and program events on HackerOne. When an event is triggered, HackerOne will send an HTTP POST payload to the webhook’s configured URL. <a href=\"https://api.hackerone.com/webhooks/#webhooks\">View the API documentation for webhooks</a>.</p>\n<p>Some examples of what webhooks can be used for include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Updating an external issue tracker</li>\n<li>Triggering a notification system</li>\n<li>Updating a report’s data backup</li>\n<li>Triggering provisioning for a user account when a hacker joins your private program</li>\n</ul>\n<p>They can be created on a program level and are bound to the permissions of the user that creates the webhook.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Webhooks are only available for Enterprise programs.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 53.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Webhooks main page\"\n        title=\"Webhooks main page\"\n        src=\"/static/0f5f4a9b5481cf57bf2fe88ed087f811/0b533/webhooks-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0f5f4a9b5481cf57bf2fe88ed087f811/fac75/webhooks-1.png 125w,\n/static/0f5f4a9b5481cf57bf2fe88ed087f811/63868/webhooks-1.png 250w,\n/static/0f5f4a9b5481cf57bf2fe88ed087f811/0b533/webhooks-1.png 500w,\n/static/0f5f4a9b5481cf57bf2fe88ed087f811/1d69c/webhooks-1.png 750w,\n/static/0f5f4a9b5481cf57bf2fe88ed087f811/00d43/webhooks-1.png 1000w,\n/static/0f5f4a9b5481cf57bf2fe88ed087f811/c1bea/webhooks-1.png 1388w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>To access webhooks go to <strong>Program Settings > Program > Webhooks</strong>.</p>\n<h3 id=\"add-a-new-webhook\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#add-a-new-webhook\" aria-label=\"add a new webhook permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Add a New Webhook</h3>\n<p>To add a new webhook:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <strong>Program Settings > Program > Webhooks</strong>.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>New webhook</strong>.</li>\n<li>Enter your <strong>Payload URL</strong>. This URL will be used to receive POST requests.</li>\n<li>Enter your webhook secret in the <strong>Secret</strong> field. The secret is used to validate that the request came from HackerOne. Learn how to <a href=\"https://api.hackerone.com/webhooks/#payloads-validating-payloads-from-hackerone\">validate the payload using a secret</a>.</li>\n<li>Select which events you’d like to trigger the webhook. You can choose between:</li>\n</ol>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Option</th>\n<th>Details</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Send me everything</td>\n<td>All events will trigger the webhook.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Let me specify individual events</td>\n<td>You can choose which events you'd like to trigger the webhook.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>Click <strong>Add webhook</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 101.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Add webhook\"\n        title=\"Add webhook\"\n        src=\"/static/46c1bdf2bab66de59e46f3ce4f7d6c60/0b533/webhooks-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/46c1bdf2bab66de59e46f3ce4f7d6c60/fac75/webhooks-2.png 125w,\n/static/46c1bdf2bab66de59e46f3ce4f7d6c60/63868/webhooks-2.png 250w,\n/static/46c1bdf2bab66de59e46f3ce4f7d6c60/0b533/webhooks-2.png 500w,\n/static/46c1bdf2bab66de59e46f3ce4f7d6c60/1d69c/webhooks-2.png 750w,\n/static/46c1bdf2bab66de59e46f3ce4f7d6c60/00d43/webhooks-2.png 1000w,\n/static/46c1bdf2bab66de59e46f3ce4f7d6c60/f868f/webhooks-2.png 1382w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"managing-webhooks\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#managing-webhooks\" aria-label=\"managing webhooks permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Managing Webhooks</h3>\n<p>To manage your webhooks:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <strong>Program Settings > Program > Webhooks</strong>.</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Edit</strong> for the webhook you want to update.</li>\n<li>Update the fields you want to change.</li>\n<li>(Optional) Select <strong>Test request</strong> to send an example request to the configured Payload URL .</li>\n<li>Click <strong>Update webhook</strong>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 108%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Test request button on Webhooks\"\n        title=\"Test request button on Webhooks\"\n        src=\"/static/febc6ac9212428af0641136863582304/0b533/webhooks-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/febc6ac9212428af0641136863582304/fac75/webhooks-3.png 125w,\n/static/febc6ac9212428af0641136863582304/63868/webhooks-3.png 250w,\n/static/febc6ac9212428af0641136863582304/0b533/webhooks-3.png 500w,\n/static/febc6ac9212428af0641136863582304/1d69c/webhooks-3.png 750w,\n/static/febc6ac9212428af0641136863582304/00d43/webhooks-3.png 1000w,\n/static/febc6ac9212428af0641136863582304/3ceac/webhooks-3.png 1456w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"view-recent-deliveries\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#view-recent-deliveries\" aria-label=\"view recent deliveries permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>View Recent Deliveries</h3>\n<p>You can view recent deliveries that have been made under the <strong>Recent deliveries</strong> section. Click on any of the deliveries to view the POST payload request.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 125.6%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"view webhook requests\"\n        title=\"view webhook requests\"\n        src=\"/static/e2890cdf9774373043d7656d6ef4b63d/0b533/webhooks-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e2890cdf9774373043d7656d6ef4b63d/fac75/webhooks-4.png 125w,\n/static/e2890cdf9774373043d7656d6ef4b63d/63868/webhooks-4.png 250w,\n/static/e2890cdf9774373043d7656d6ef4b63d/0b533/webhooks-4.png 500w,\n/static/e2890cdf9774373043d7656d6ef4b63d/1d69c/webhooks-4.png 750w,\n/static/e2890cdf9774373043d7656d6ef4b63d/00d43/webhooks-4.png 1000w,\n/static/e2890cdf9774373043d7656d6ef4b63d/f09ab/webhooks-4.png 1250w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Click on the <strong>Response</strong> tab to view the payload responses.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 102.4%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"view webhook responses\"\n        title=\"view webhook responses\"\n        src=\"/static/b48d93f3ac2c6cb3414407a8180551e7/0b533/webhooks-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b48d93f3ac2c6cb3414407a8180551e7/fac75/webhooks-5.png 125w,\n/static/b48d93f3ac2c6cb3414407a8180551e7/63868/webhooks-5.png 250w,\n/static/b48d93f3ac2c6cb3414407a8180551e7/0b533/webhooks-5.png 500w,\n/static/b48d93f3ac2c6cb3414407a8180551e7/1d69c/webhooks-5.png 750w,\n/static/b48d93f3ac2c6cb3414407a8180551e7/00d43/webhooks-5.png 1000w,\n/static/b48d93f3ac2c6cb3414407a8180551e7/afa26/webhooks-5.png 1258w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/programs/webhooks.html","id":"programs/webhooks","title":"Webhooks","description":null},"headings":[{"value":"Add a New Webhook"},{"value":"Managing Webhooks"},{"value":"View Recent Deliveries"}]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}